,"msg":"單嘢真係好撚癲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:34:11.000Z","msg":"香港已經發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086ec933ce049c729840b5b10d0e158f04de4642","tid":2151294,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e74c8395ebe25a7ba47f43b12857b6d24b243396","tid":2151294,"uid":46906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:21:20.000Z","msg":"拉晒最有領導力既留低果個真係比人夾硬推上馬，好鬼慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />和理非底但個局勢已經迫到和勇要不分，最後都係要流亡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:35:39.000Z","msg":"女人一個都好勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc737f64e786fff958439498e7de6bf2a27c79ef","tid":2151294,"uid":207826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:35:43.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"efb87e33cbc5fdfe2f7be5e9ea95d68c70070a2d","tid":2151294,"uid":174322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3094802bbd4f7f4bd709e4349ec93084606dfd9d","tid":2151294,"uid":218158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:31:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://europechinese.blogspot.com/2020/08/blog-post_11.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feuropechinese.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F08%2Fblog-post_11.html&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FiZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=fb242ba6\" target=\"_blank\">https://europechinese.blogspot.com/2020/08/blog-post_11.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:40:21.000Z","msg":"//盧卡申科在1999年跟當時的俄羅斯總統葉利欽（Boris Yeltsin）簽署了聯合條約，條約訂明，白俄和俄國最終會組成一個邦聯，有一個包括了兩國總統、總理、議會的高級理事會，兩國有共同貨幣、聯合軍隊、聯合公民身份等等，跡近變成一個國家。//<br />\n<br />\nDiu雖然唔應該同一國兩制類比，但，咁咪啫係USSR 2.0?<br />\n<br />\n//但目前的反對派卻普遍親俄，或起碼對俄羅斯及普京不反感。例如被取消參選資格的前駐美國大使Valery Tsepkalo，他目前流亡的國家是俄國。<br />\n<br />\n由此可見，白俄目前的反政府示威跟大家傳統認知的顏色革命完全是兩碼子事。<br />\n<br />\n所以，對普京而言，他是可以接受白俄「變天」的，只要換上來的新領導人&mdash;&mdash;例如目前的反對派領袖Sviatlana Tsikhanouskaya&mdash;&mdash;同樣維持與俄國友好。//<br />\n<br />\nCLS, 啫係唯一嘅選項其實都係伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85aa7dc42b9de104e9364a7ff16695e73a4ab32c","tid":2151294,"uid":174322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aad6787de2ea1bfa49f189027f656ca06567b2f","tid":2151294,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9405c93dd547ee92486645daee8a8afe78d41d91","tid":2151294,"uid":174322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:20:44.000Z","msg":"單嘢真係好撚癲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:34:11.000Z","msg":"香港已經發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:41:09.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8694c398a0733837a2d1cbef42f5f5180c67238a","tid":2151294,"uid":174322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:46:01.000Z","msg":"推多十五分鐘"},{"pid":"7451b78c856cf876e09fc183e645218f115b8c90","tid":2151294,"uid":174322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:46:42.000Z","msg":"都冇咩人睇就由個po 自然死"},{"pid":"9080290af1346cf908e110593740cc33c7f3a18f","tid":2151294,"uid":284429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ae73ded93fbae3d1f1628d6dec3bc030322e94","tid":2151294,"uid":254246,"like":