s/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:31:12.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭都係綁架有名氣嘅人,兼搞佢屋企人"},{"pid":"78b95640c8427a27403c18c9e078e6030bbe5487","tid":2151294,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"efb87e33cbc5fdfe2f7be5e9ea95d68c70070a2d","tid":2151294,"uid":174322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3094802bbd4f7f4bd709e4349ec93084606dfd9d","tid":2151294,"uid":218158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:31:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://europechinese.blogspot.com/2020/08/blog-post_11.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feuropechinese.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F08%2Fblog-post_11.html&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FiZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=fb242ba6\" target=\"_blank\">https://europechinese.blogspot.com/2020/08/blog-post_11.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T10:40:21.000Z","msg":"//盧卡申科在1999年跟當時的俄羅斯總統葉利欽（Boris Yeltsin）簽署了聯合條約，條約訂明，白俄和俄國最終會組成一個邦聯，有一個包括了兩國總統、總理、議會的高級理事會，兩國有共同貨幣、聯合軍隊、聯合公民身份等等，跡近變成一個國家。//<br />\n<br />\nDiu雖然唔應該同一國兩制類比，但，咁咪啫係USSR 2.0?<br />\n<br />\n//但目前的反對派卻普遍親俄，或起碼對俄羅斯及普京不反感。例如被取消參選資格的前駐美國大使Valery Tsepkalo，他目前流亡的國家是俄國。<br />\n<br />\n由此可見，白俄目前的反政府示威跟大家傳統認知的顏色革命完全是兩碼子事。<br />\n<br />\n所以，對普京而言，他是可以接受白俄「變天」的，只要換上來的新領導人&mdash;&mdash;例如目前的反對派領袖Sviatlana Tsikhanouskaya&mdash;&mdash;同樣維持與俄國友好。//<br />\n<br />\nCLS, 啫係唯一嘅選項其實都係伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T12:33:26.000Z","msg":"咪又係蘇共式扶植個政權出嚟,話就話解體,事實上蘇共極權從來無消失過,蛾狗一樣係耐唔耐就搞周邊國家"},{"pid":"48df75871ac3564736e079d6c7d809038e79a6c9","tid":2151294,"uid":174322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d339d2b3323dc2c22a97216